long.ar:
IG Comment Export Tool is free to export comments from Instagram to a csv file. No registration or payment required! Totally Free!

How It Works?
1. Enter link to a Instagram post
2. Click "EXPORT COMMENTS" button

Features:
1. Export UNLIMITED comments
2. Save as CSV

What Columns You Can Export?
#username
#username id
#profile url
#profile pic url
#comment id
#comment text
#comment time

Data Privacy:
All data processing is handled locally on your computer and does not pass through our web server, guaranteeing total privacy and security.

Disclaimer:
SocialDeck - IG Comment Export Tool is a third-party extension that simplifies the process of exporting Instagram comments and related data, enabling improved analytics and management. Please note that this tool is not developed by, endorsed by, or officially associated with Instagram, Inc.

Note:
To safeguard your primary Instagram account from temporary restrictions, we strongly suggest creating a dedicated account for data export activities. This approach helps minimize the risk of disruptions to your regular Instagram usage while keeping your primary account secure.

long.nl:
IG Comment Export Tool is free to export comments from Instagram to a csv file. No registration or payment required! Totally Free!

How It Works?
1. Enter link to a Instagram post
2. Click "EXPORT COMMENTS" button

Features:
1. Export UNLIMITED comments
2. Save as CSV

What Columns You Can Export?
#username
#username id
#profile url
#profile pic url
#comment id
#comment text
#comment time

Data Privacy:
All data processing is handled locally on your computer and does not pass through our web server, guaranteeing total privacy and security.

Disclaimer:
SocialDeck - IG Comment Export Tool is a third-party extension that simplifies the process of exporting Instagram comments and related data, enabling improved analytics and management. Please note that this tool is not developed by, endorsed by, or officially associated with Instagram, Inc.

Note:
To safeguard your primary Instagram account from temporary restrictions, we strongly suggest creating a dedicated account for data export activities. This approach helps minimize the risk of disruptions to your regular Instagram usage while keeping your primary account secure.
